title: Call or Text Great Rental Property!!! Located in very quiet community
posting_body: ['Great Rental Property!!!', 'Located in very quiet community at end of cul-de-sac with Passive Park right next door.', 'Excellent condition, this popular Darby 4 model offers master bedroom suite downstairs, 3 bedrooms upstairs.', 'Private screened brick paved patio, crown moldings throughout main living area.', 'Built-in shelves in Dining an Family Room Areas, Laundry Room.', 'Community pool and recreational area in the heart of the community of The Lakes.', 'Easy access to schools, major roads, shops and restaurants.', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'Helping people find rentals since 2012!', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'We specialize in Broward County Rentals.', 'I can text you a list of all the rentals available in the area.', 'Fast approval, NO HOA for some properties.', 'Pet friendly for some!', 'Proof of income is the most  important thing.', 'We can help people with bad credit or no credit!', "Let me know what you're looking for and I will find the right place regardless of the situation!", 'Brittini Flinn', 'SUN OCEAN REALTY', 'NO EMAIL', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'PLEASE REFER TO TYN112460601']
